<div class="intro">
<div class="welcome">
Welcome to ECS, the School  of Electronics and Computer Science at the University of Southampton. ECS is one of the world's leading centres for 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050108083920/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/research/">research</a>, 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050108083920/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/about/teaching/">teaching</a>, <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050108083920/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/business/">enterprise and innovation</a> in Electronics, Electrical Engineering and Computer Science.
<div class="sig">Head of School: <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050108083920/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/people/wh">Professor Wendy Hall</a></div>
</div>
<div class="headline"><a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050108083920/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/668"><img src="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050108083920im_/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/image.php?id=news_668_img&amp;maxw=200&amp;maxh=150&amp;corners=10&amp;edge=1&amp;checksum=0e7e17639140dd0d8eb1011fbe269a75&amp;fn=fn.png" alt="Professor Tony Hey" border="0" width="108" height="150" class="thumbnail" /></a><h2>Headline News</h2><h3><a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050108083920/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/668">CBE for former Head of School</a></h3><p>Professor Tony Hey, a senior member of the School of Electronics and Computer Science, who is currently on secondment from the School as Director of the UK's E-Science Programme, was awarded a CBE in the New Year's Honours List for services to science.</p></div></div><div class='rightside'>

